name: Turbo
description:
Turbo Action is a side scrolling beat’em up video games, inspired
by the famous ‘Street of Rage’ 1991.
Street of rage is first game that I played on Sega in the 90s at
Jakarta (Indonesia). Growing up in Jakarta , where most of the
country’s prosperity was centralized, especially in the
entertainment industry.
We all love watching television for watch the news, politics,
religion, gossip, Quiz and cartoons.
Everything was centralized into a television channel,
But Sometimes television Centralised system can be a media
propaganda to made a stereotype or even made people
disunited for their freedom.
